{"type": "article", "id": 30458, "title": "太阳能供电的夹克", "description": "", "date": "2016-08-02T23:04:43Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 39, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160802174853vISozmpXVg0BQenT.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>在荷兰瓦登群岛（Wadden）上，当地导游会带领旅行者进行长达 2 到 10 小时徒步探险。当地工作人员特意邀请可穿戴技术设计师 <a href=\"http://paulinevandongen.nl/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Pauline van Dongen</a> 和可持续服装品牌 <a href=\"http://www.bluelooporiginals.eu/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Blue Loop Originals</a> 为导游们打造了一件太阳能供电的夹克，在挡风遮雨的同时还能为便携设备进行充电。夹克上安装了三块薄膜式的太阳能电池板和感应式充电系统，根据不同的天气情况可以为智能手机无线充电 1 到 2 小时，其他设备则可以通过 USB 传输线进行充电。在强大的功能性之外，太阳能电池板本身也成为了夹克的美学特征，看上去科技感十足。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160802174916APaNUR356g7pnJBx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160802174915Q5tY9JBK6naRlDrU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160802174916QcdDxbUevmX2tW0N.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160802174916UdNiWRgE7pSwsI3e.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}